import React from 'react';
import { View, Text, StyleSheet, Image } from 'react-native';

const LocationHeader = () => {
    return (
        <View style={styles.location_Header}>
            <View style={styles.location_Header_box}>
                <Text style={styles.l_left}> 9:45</Text>
                <Text style={styles.l_middle}>
                    <Text style={styles.l__middle}>edrftgyuhj</Text>
                </Text>
                <Text style={styles.l_right}>
                    <Image source={require("../../../assets/hd2.webp")} style={{ width: '20px', height: '100%', margin: 2 }} />
                    <Image source={require("../../../assets/hd3.png")} style={{ width: '22px', height: '100%', margin: 2 }} />
                    <Image source={require("../../../assets/hd1.webp")} style={{ width: '20px', height: '100%', margin: 2 }} />
                </Text>
                <View style={styles.bottomStyle}>
                    <Image source={require("../../../assets/sci1.png")} style={styles.b_imgStyle} color="#fff" />
                    <Text style={styles.b_textStyle}>Select Location</Text>
                    <Image source={require("../../../assets/sci2.png")} style={styles.b_imgStyle} />
                </View>
            </View>
        </View>
    );
}

    l__middle: {

        height: "200px",
        opacity: '0.5px',

    l_right: {

    },b_imgStyle,im

export default LocationHeader;
